title: Partisan
desc:
- Can be played on <:yellow:1106234135384699023>. Can also be played on any card with the permission of the one who played that card.
- If you win and you've played one or more <:partisan:1107460550268559380> cards, choose a player. They may discard up to that many cards. Then, if they have one or less cards in hand, they win as well. There can still be another runner-up.
